('c74a5cdb', 'West Bandung Adventure', 'west-bandung-adventure', 'One day trip exploring the beautiful scenery of West Bandung. Packages including 1 deluxe room, tour guides, transportation from and to the hotel, 1x Lunch, 1x Dinner, and tickets to Sanghiyang Heuleut, Goa Pawon, and Stone Garden.\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n-Bhara', 1800000, 0, '1', 1, NULL, NULL),
